<b>Client-Server</b> application that provides acccess to an <b>online library</b>.
Users can search the books based on different filters:

- genre
- author
- title
- year
- ISBN
- rating

They can also download or upload books in pdf format.
Every user activity(book search, book access, book download) is stored in a mysql database and, based on this info, the server provides <b>book suggestions</b>.

The suggestions are based on various factors such as:
- user preferences
- similar users(that have similar book preferences)
- book rating

The <b>book suggestions algorithm</b> becomes better as user activity grows.

